Marley Overman with Illustrated Properties and Gary Pohrer with Serhant had the listing. Pohrer also brought the buyer. Mondre is the co-CEO of Menlo Park, California-based private equity firm Silver Lake, which has $110 billion in assets under management, according to published reports.
